1.1 Security controls
      technical controls
          -controls implemented using systems
          -operating system controls
          -firewals,antivirus
      Managerial controls
          -Administrative controls associated with secuirity design and implementation
          -security policies,standard operating  procdedures
      operational controls
          -controls implemented by people insted of systems
          -security guards, awarenes programs
      physical controls
          -limit physical access
          -gurad shack
          -fenchs,locks
          -badge readers
